\begin_layout Standard
设整数 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 (
\begin_inset Formula $n>1$
\end_inset

) 恰有 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

 个互不相同的素因子, 记 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 的所有正约数之和为 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma(n)$
\end_inset

.
 证明: 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma(n)\mid(2n-k)!$
\end_inset

.
